description: Lupang Hinirang (Chosen Land) is the official national anthem of The Philippines. Its music was composed in the year 1898 by Julián Felipe, with lyrics in Spanish adapted from the poem Filipinas, written by José Palma in the year 1899.
title: Lupang Hinirang
